ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2011-12
PrecisAppointment of HEATHER CRUDEN as High Commissioner for Canada to the People’s Republic of Bangladesh; CHANTAL DE VARENNES as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Côte d’Ivoire; DAVID DRAKE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Arab Republic of Egypt; WELDON EPP as Consul General of Canada in Guangzhou (People’s Republic of China); TRUDY KERNIGHAN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Togolese Republic, with residence in Accra; JEAN-CAROL PELLETIER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Democratic Republic of the Congo; and LISA STADELBAUER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Zimbabwe, with concurrent accreditation as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Botswana.
